{"id":759,"date":"2020-07-06T14:13:32","date_gmt":"2020-07-06T13:13:32","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/?post_type=module&#038;p=759"},"modified":"2020-07-08T02:28:35","modified_gmt":"2020-07-08T01:28:35","slug":"fundamentals","status":"publish","type":"module","link":"https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/module\/google-algorithms\/fundamentals","title":{"rendered":"The Fundamentals"},"featured_media":0,"parent":387,"menu_order":13,"template":"","acf":{"module_quiz":"","module_time":"15","module_difficulty":{"value":"easy","label":"Easy"},"module_short_description":"<p>Before we take a deep dive into the algorithms themselves, let\u2019s take a refresher on some of the concepts that make up the cleverness of Google.<\/p>\n","module_long_description":"<p>Before we take a deep dive into the algorithms themselves, let\u2019s take a refresher on some of the concepts that make up the cleverness of Google. In this module, we're introducing some basic terminology and doing the introduction to the most sophisticated artificial formula in the world - Google Algorithm.<\/p>\n","video_file":false,"video_url":"","content":"<h2>What Is An Algorithm?<\/h2>\n<p>In its simplest definition, an algorithm is a set of rules to follow in order to solve a problem. For example, in the real world, the algorithm for making a cake is its recipe. In computer science, an algorithm is defined as a program with step-by-step instructions to solve a problem.<\/p>\n<img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-762\" src=\"https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/What-Is-An-Algorithm-.jpg\" alt=\"What Is An Algorithm?\" width=\"1680\" height=\"1176\" srcset=\"https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/What-Is-An-Algorithm-.jpg 1680w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/What-Is-An-Algorithm--1536x1075.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/What-Is-An-Algorithm--57x40.jpg 57w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/What-Is-An-Algorithm--114x80.jpg 114w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/What-Is-An-Algorithm--43x30.jpg 43w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/What-Is-An-Algorithm--86x60.jpg 86w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/What-Is-An-Algorithm--34x24.jpg 34w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/What-Is-An-Algorithm--69x48.jpg 69w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/What-Is-An-Algorithm--26x18.jpg 26w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/What-Is-An-Algorithm--51x36.jpg 51w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1680px) 100vw, 1680px\" \/>\n<h2>What is Artificial Intelligence?<\/h2>\n<p>Artificial intelligence (AI for short) is a branch of computer science that refers to the simulation of human intelligence by a computer.<\/p>\n<img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-771\" src=\"https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/What-is-Artificial-Intelligence-.jpg\" alt=\"What is Artificial Intelligence\" width=\"1670\" height=\"1176\" srcset=\"https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/What-is-Artificial-Intelligence-.jpg 1670w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/What-is-Artificial-Intelligence--1536x1082.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/What-is-Artificial-Intelligence--57x40.jpg 57w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/What-is-Artificial-Intelligence--114x80.jpg 114w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/What-is-Artificial-Intelligence--43x30.jpg 43w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/What-is-Artificial-Intelligence--85x60.jpg 85w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/What-is-Artificial-Intelligence--34x24.jpg 34w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/What-is-Artificial-Intelligence--68x48.jpg 68w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/What-is-Artificial-Intelligence--26x18.jpg 26w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/What-is-Artificial-Intelligence--51x36.jpg 51w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1670px) 100vw, 1670px\" \/>\n<h2>What is Machine Learning?<\/h2>\n<p>Machine learning is an application of artificial intelligence where a computer teaches itself how to perform a specific task instead of being taught or programmed to do so by humans.<\/p>\n<img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-772\" src=\"https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/What-is-Machine-Learning-.jpg\" alt=\"What is Machine Learning\" width=\"1489\" height=\"1128\" srcset=\"https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/What-is-Machine-Learning-.jpg 1489w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/What-is-Machine-Learning--53x40.jpg 53w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/What-is-Machine-Learning--106x80.jpg 106w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/What-is-Machine-Learning--40x30.jpg 40w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/What-is-Machine-Learning--79x60.jpg 79w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/What-is-Machine-Learning--32x24.jpg 32w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/What-is-Machine-Learning--63x48.jpg 63w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/What-is-Machine-Learning--24x18.jpg 24w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/What-is-Machine-Learning--48x36.jpg 48w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1489px) 100vw, 1489px\" \/>\n<h2>What Is A Neural Network?<\/h2>\n<p>A neural network is made up of a set of algorithms modelled loosely after the human brain, that are designed to recognize patterns.<\/p>\n<img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-773\" src=\"https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/What-Is-A-Neural-Network-.jpg\" alt=\"What Is A Neural Network-\" width=\"1694\" height=\"1236\" srcset=\"https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/What-Is-A-Neural-Network-.jpg 1694w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/What-Is-A-Neural-Network--1536x1121.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/What-Is-A-Neural-Network--55x40.jpg 55w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/What-Is-A-Neural-Network--110x80.jpg 110w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/What-Is-A-Neural-Network--41x30.jpg 41w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/What-Is-A-Neural-Network--82x60.jpg 82w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/What-Is-A-Neural-Network--33x24.jpg 33w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/What-Is-A-Neural-Network--66x48.jpg 66w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/What-Is-A-Neural-Network--25x18.jpg 25w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/What-Is-A-Neural-Network--49x36.jpg 49w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1694px) 100vw, 1694px\" \/>\n<h2>What is a Google Algorithm?<\/h2>\n<p>Unsurprisingly, Google algorithms follow the same basic definition and rule of an algorithm that we defined earlier. Google has its own set of incredibly complex and sophisticated algorithms for deciding which pages should appear for a particular search query.<\/p>\n<p>In order to achieve this, Google\u2019s search algorithms look at many factors such as the relevance and usability of your web pages, the load speed of your pages etc. Each ranking factor is given a different weight which varies depending on the nature of the search query. For instance, the freshness of the content is more important for current news topics, than it is for dictionary definitions.<\/p>\n<p>These algorithms utilize the power of artificial intelligence, machine learning and (in some cases) neural networks to determine everything from minutiae like the topical relevance of page titles to the more complex problems like natural language processing. In doing so, Google\u2019s algorithms are constantly changing and evolving which means that Google now makes thousands of changes to its algorithms every year. Most of these updates are incredibly subtle and go unnoticed, but every now and then, Google will roll out major algorithmic updates that significantly impact the search results &#8211; these are referred to as core algorithm updates, which we\u2019ll tackle very shortly!<\/p>\n<img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-651\" src=\"https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Googlebot.jpg\" alt=\"Googlebot\" width=\"1260\" height=\"987\" srcset=\"https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Googlebot.jpg 1260w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Googlebot-51x40.jpg 51w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Googlebot-102x80.jpg 102w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Googlebot-38x30.jpg 38w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Googlebot-77x60.jpg 77w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Googlebot-31x24.jpg 31w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Googlebot-61x48.jpg 61w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Googlebot-23x18.jpg 23w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Googlebot-46x36.jpg 46w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1260px) 100vw, 1260px\" \/>\n"},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/modules\/759"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/modules"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/module"}],"version-history":[{"count":9,"href":"https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/modules\/759\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":774,"href":"https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/modules\/759\/revisions\/774"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/modules\/387"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=759"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}